flowchart TD
    A["Anyone taps +<br/>title + optional note/photo<br/>2 taps"] --> B["Choose target vertical<br/>(any vertical, even not their own)"]
    A --> OPT["Optional: escalate flag<br/>+ tag people who should decide"]
    B --> C["Lead's triage queue"]
    C --> D{"Lead decides"}
    D -->|"file it"| E["Becomes a task<br/>under an objective<br/>or floating in vertical"]
    D -->|"needs decision"| F["Escalate to Admin<br/>with comments + suggestions"]
    D -->|"ask around"| G["Request suggestions<br/>from tagged people"]
    G --> D
    F --> E
    C -.->|"unresolved > 2 days"| H["Reminder to Lead"]
    H -.->|"still unresolved"| I["Flagged to Admin"]
    E --> S["Creator always sees status:<br/>pending / resolved<br/>+ can comment inside their token"]
    C --> S
